00:10:27,194 --> 00:10:29,196
and see where
Joey's education went wrong.

260
00:10:29,229 --> 00:10:30,831
Right.

261
00:10:32,332 --> 00:10:34,201
LINDA:
Okay, that was weird.

262
00:10:34,234 --> 00:10:35,703
Is it...

263
00:10:35,736 --> 00:10:37,270
weird for...

264
00:10:37,304 --> 00:10:38,972
us to be friends?

265
00:10:39,006 --> 00:10:41,308
No.

266
00:10:41,341 --> 00:10:43,310
Of course not.

267
00:10:43,343 --> 00:10:44,812
I mean, can't a...

268
00:10:44,845 --> 00:10:48,081
Can't a woman
be friends with a...

269
00:10:48,115 --> 00:10:50,083
with a brilliant,

270
00:10:50,117 --> 00:10:52,185
tall,

271
00:10:52,219 --> 00:10:54,054
gorgeous angel?

272
00:10:54,087 --> 00:10:57,224
Well, can't an angel
be friends with a...

273
00:10:57,257 --> 00:11:00,393
amazing, accomplished...

274
00:11:01,294 --> 00:11:03,330
...beautiful,

275
00:11:03,363 --> 00:11:05,966
and passionate woman?

276
00:11:19,346 --> 00:11:21,281
Um...

277
00:11:21,314 --> 00:11:24,084
