you're defending me.

305
00:12:28,481 --> 00:12:30,283
Look, Frankie,
I'm not your lawyer.

306
00:12:30,317 --> 00:12:31,919
I'm the prosecutor.

307
00:12:31,952 --> 00:12:33,520
I work with
the cops now.

308
00:12:33,553 --> 00:12:34,922
Against you.

309
00:12:34,955 --> 00:12:36,423
What's the world coming to?

310
00:12:36,456 --> 00:12:37,791
Yeah, tell me about it.

311
00:12:37,825 --> 00:12:38,926
LUCIFER: What
happened, Frankie?

312
00:12:38,959 --> 00:12:41,194
You were supposed to
mentor Joey Pileggi,

313
00:12:41,228 --> 00:12:42,295
not kill him.

314
00:12:42,329 --> 00:12:43,931
I got no idea about any killing.

315
00:12:43,964 --> 00:12:45,465
LUCIFER: Oh, did
Joey steal from you,

316
00:12:45,498 --> 00:12:47,267
so you made
a brutal example of him?

317
00:12:47,300 --> 00:12:48,468
Well, guess what?

318
00:12:48,501 --> 00:12:51,104
I love making brutal
examples of people.

319
00:12:51,138 --> 00:12:52,105
Like I said,

320
00:12:52,139 --> 00:12:54,908
I don't know any Joey,
and I don't know you.

321
00:12:56,409 --> 00:12:58,511
CHLOE:
You do know him.

322
00:13:01,281 --> 00:13:03,216
Yeah, I might've seen him once.

323
00:13:03,250 --> 00:13:04,384
It's hard to say.

324
00:13:04,417 --> 00:13:07,855
Is it true you're the head
of the Ferrante mob family?

325
00:13:07,888 --> 00:13:09,189
LUCIFER:
Well, come on.

326
00:13:09,222 --> 00:13:12,025
Answer her.
You do not need to answer that.

327
00:13:12,059 --> 00:13:13,226
I don't?

328
00:13:14,862 --> 00:13:17,064
But it would be helpful
if you did.

329
00:13:17,097 --> 00:13:18,932
Right. Enough of this
"bad cop, worse cop."

330
00:13:18,966 --> 00:13:21,468
Tell me, Frankie.

331
00:13:21,501 --> 00:13:23,270
What is it you really want?

332
00:13:24,905 --> 00:13:27,374
I want to find out
who killed little Joey,

333
00:13:27,407 --> 00:13:29,309
and I want payback.

334
00:13:30,443 --> 00:13:32,379
Oh.

335
00:13:34,314 --> 00:13:35,916
He was...

336
00:13:35,949 --> 00:13:37,517
He was such a good kid,
that Joey.

337
00:13:37,550 --> 00:13:39,352
A real go-getter.

338
00:13:39,386 --> 00:13:41,254
We all loved him.
He had a real bright future.

339
00:13:41,288 --> 00:13:43,957
We found quite a bit
of contraband on him.

340
00:13:45,125 --> 00:13:47,260
Did he ever steal anything
from you?

341
00:13:47,294 --> 00:13:48,962
Joey? Never.

342
00:13:48,996 --> 00:13:51,331
Everything he had
he got from us.

343
00:13:51,364 --> 00:13:53,200
Oh, quite the lavish employers,
aren't you?

344
00:13:53,233 --> 00:13:56,303
Hey, me and the fellas, we're
real generous to our family.

345
00:13:56,336 --> 00:13:58,605
'Cause that's
who he was: family.

346
00:14:00,073 --> 00:14:02,342
If there's anything I can do
to help with Joey's killer,

347
00:14:02,375 --> 00:14:05,045
