That means he would kill him.

349
00:14:07,114 --> 00:14:09,616
Oh, thank you, Charlotte.

350
00:14:11,218 --> 00:14:13,520
Thanks.

351
00:14:13,553 --> 00:14:16,056
Hey, Chloe?
Yes.

352
00:14:16,089 --> 00:14:17,925
(Dan clears throat)

353
00:14:17,958 --> 00:14:19,426
I don't think
Frankie's our guy.

354
00:14:19,459 --> 00:14:20,961
His alibi checks out.

355
00:14:20,994 --> 00:14:23,430
Look what just came in.

356
00:14:23,463 --> 00:14:25,298
Lucifer.

357
00:14:25,332 --> 00:14:26,666
We got another body.

358
00:14:26,699 --> 00:14:28,368
Let's go.

359
00:14:37,244 --> 00:14:40,080
Double tap to the chest,
just like Joey.

360
00:14:40,113 --> 00:14:43,383
Detective, I know
this woman.

361
00:14:43,416 --> 00:14:44,584
What?

362
00:14:44,617 --> 00:14:47,354
I did her a favor,
too, years ago.

363
00:14:47,387 --> 00:14:51,358
This isn't just a murder.
It's another message.

364
00:14:51,391 --> 00:14:53,393
For me.

365
00:14:56,596 --> 00:14:59,666
Someone was definitely
sending a message.

366
00:14:59,699 --> 00:15:01,201
Frieda Marquez, 36.

367
00:15:01,234 --> 00:15:04,471
The noose was made
out of her own hair.

368
00:15:04,504 --> 00:15:06,073
How twisted is that?

369
00:15:06,106 --> 00:15:08,208
But hanging wasn't
what killed her.

370
00:15:08,241 --> 00:15:10,210
She died from two
gunshots to the chest.

371
00:15:10,243 --> 00:15:12,245
So the killer arranged her
after he killed her,

372
00:15:12,279 --> 00:15:13,013
just like with Joey.

373
00:15:13,046 --> 00:15:14,982
LUCIFER: We need
to find the man

374
00:15:15,015 --> 00:15:16,249
who did this
and punish him.

375
00:15:16,283 --> 00:15:18,018
CHLOE: Lucifer, what
do you know about her?

376
00:15:18,051 --> 00:15:20,220
Frieda wanted to become a
hairstylist to the stars,

377
00:15:20,253 --> 00:15:23,523
so I made a few choice
introductions, that's all.

378
00:15:23,556 --> 00:15:26,126
I can't believe you knew Frieda.

379
00:15:26,159 --> 00:15:27,995
Her hair products are huge.

380
00:15:28,028 --> 00:15:29,963
She had salons
all over the city,

381
00:15:29,997 --> 00:15:31,564
