382
00:15:31,598 --> 00:15:33,400
I use her finishing
cream every day.

383
00:15:33,433 --> 00:15:36,169
Right. Well, then I guess
she got what she wanted.

384
00:15:36,203 --> 00:15:37,137
Until now.

385
00:15:37,170 --> 00:15:39,406
