Thanks, Ella.

386
00:15:39,439 --> 00:15:41,008
Can I talk to you?

387
00:15:41,041 --> 00:15:44,177
If these messages really are
for you, I'm worried.

388
00:15:44,211 --> 00:15:45,412
Who's sending them?

389
00:15:45,445 --> 00:15:47,147
What are they trying to say?

390
00:15:47,180 --> 00:15:49,349
Detective, I wasn't
entirely forthcoming earlier.

391
00:15:49,382 --> 00:15:52,585
The real reason I started
granting favors again

392
00:15:52,619 --> 00:15:54,254
was because of the Sinnerman.

393
00:15:54,287 --> 00:15:56,623
