that this guy really exists.

396
00:16:00,260 --> 00:16:02,229
Well, now might be the time
to become a believer,

397
00:16:02,262 --> 00:16:05,132
because this appears to be his
way of escalating our rivalry.

398
00:16:05,165 --> 00:16:07,067
You think this is the same guy
that kidnapped you

399
00:16:07,100 --> 00:16:08,268
and dumped you in the desert?

400
00:16:08,301 --> 00:16:10,703
Amongst other things, yes.
Okay, well,

401
00:16:10,737 --> 00:16:12,305
I'm gonna need proof
that this guy is real.

402
00:16:12,339 --> 00:16:13,506
