Oh, he is real.

403
00:16:13,540 --> 00:16:15,142
And very dangerous.

404
00:16:15,175 --> 00:16:16,709
His organization has
been wreaking havoc

405
00:16:16,743 --> 00:16:18,445
in the Midwest for years.

406
00:16:18,478 --> 00:16:21,348
I ran into him in Chicago.
I couldn't get my hands on him.

407
00:16:21,381 --> 00:16:23,716
See? It's the one thing
the lieutenant and I agree on:

408
00:16:23,750 --> 00:16:24,717
our common enemy,

409
00:16:24,751 --> 00:16:26,453
the Sinnerman.

410
00:16:26,486 --> 00:16:27,654
So you two discussed this?

411
00:16:27,687 --> 00:16:29,122
When were you gonna fill me in?

412
00:16:29,156 --> 00:16:30,557
It's a need-to-know basis
only, Decker.

413
00:16:30,590 --> 00:16:31,624
Feel free to blame me.

414
00:16:31,658 --> 00:16:33,726
Hmm.
The thing is,

415
00:16:33,760 --> 00:16:35,395
