like the Sinnerman.

416
00:16:35,428 --> 00:16:37,197
He kills for power
and influence.
(phone vibrates)

417
00:16:37,230 --> 00:16:39,466
Taunting a nightclub
owner seems petty, small.

418
00:16:39,499 --> 00:16:42,235
Well, perhaps you don't know
the full story.

419
00:16:43,770 --> 00:16:45,438
Okay, we're gonna
treat this murder

420
00:16:45,472 --> 00:16:46,773
as we would any other crime:

421
00:16:46,806 --> 00:16:48,775
