till we find the truth,

422
00:16:48,808 --> 00:16:50,310
Sinnerman or not.

423
00:16:50,343 --> 00:16:53,080
Sorry, but I don't
have time for that.

424
00:16:53,113 --> 00:16:53,780
Lucifer,

425
00:16:53,813 --> 00:16:55,348
