this Sinnerman fellow.

430
00:17:05,258 --> 00:17:08,361
I'd appreciate your help.
Call me back.

431
00:17:08,395 --> 00:17:10,497
Oh, also, it's Lucifer.

432
00:17:10,530 --> 00:17:12,332
Good luck with that.

433
00:17:12,365 --> 00:17:15,068
He's probably too busy
with Linda to answer.

434
00:17:15,102 --> 00:17:17,237
Mazikeen, you're back!

435
00:17:17,270 --> 00:17:19,506
(chuckles)
I love the hair.

436
00:17:19,539 --> 00:17:21,108
Can we talk?

437
00:17:21,141 --> 00:17:23,243
We certainly can.
Good timing. I need your help.

438
00:17:23,276 --> 00:17:25,212
Hang on. Do you even care
what I was about to say?

439
00:17:25,245 --> 00:17:27,780
Of course I do. It's just that
my current problem is important.

440
00:17:27,814 --> 00:17:30,117
