my thing isn't important?

441
00:17:30,150 --> 00:17:31,784
Okay. Fine. What is it?

442
00:17:31,818 --> 00:17:33,153
Did...
(phone vibrates)

443
00:17:33,186 --> 00:17:35,155
(sighs)
Sorry, just...

444
00:17:35,188 --> 00:17:37,724
(groans) Telemarketers. They've
been hounding me all day.

445
00:17:37,757 --> 00:17:39,626
