Our second vic, Frieda--

454
00:17:58,845 --> 00:18:00,413
total fighter.

455
00:18:00,447 --> 00:18:02,282
She struggled with the killer
and scratched him.

456
00:18:02,315 --> 00:18:05,485
So I checked out her fingernail
