458
00:18:07,254 --> 00:18:09,222
And came up
with the killer's DNA.

459
00:18:09,256 --> 00:18:11,591
Which matches a hair that
I recovered from Joey's place.

460
00:18:11,624 --> 00:18:13,226
So, boom,

461
00:18:13,260 --> 00:18:15,295
