at both scenes.

462
00:18:15,328 --> 00:18:18,165
But, that's not even
the cool part.

463
00:18:18,198 --> 00:18:21,568
I did some more digging
and found a perfect match

464
00:18:21,601 --> 00:18:23,436
with a blood spatter sample

465
00:18:23,470 --> 00:18:25,405
from an old Sinnerman case

466
00:18:25,438 --> 00:18:26,639
in Chicago.

467
00:18:26,673 --> 00:18:29,876
Proving that Pierce's Sinnerman
really is operating in L.A.

468
00:18:29,909 --> 00:18:31,778
Ella, you're a miracle worker.

469
00:18:31,811 --> 00:18:33,413
Aw, no biggie.

470
00:18:33,446 --> 00:18:36,583
My peeps in Detroit made
some calls to Chicago PD for me.

471
00:18:36,616 --> 00:18:39,186
Meant hours of sifting
through case files, but,

472
00:18:39,219 --> 00:18:40,687
you know, I just put on

473
00:18:40,720 --> 00:18:43,223
my Beastie Boys
and powered through.

474
00:18:45,458 --> 00:18:48,461
Decker, did you hear
what I said?

475
00:18:48,495 --> 00:18:49,462
