476
00:18:49,496 --> 00:18:50,830
Hmm? Sorry. No.

477
00:18:50,863 --> 00:18:53,166
Aw, never mind.

478
00:18:54,267 --> 00:18:55,568
Man, I can't believe nothing

479
00:18:55,602 --> 00:18:57,737
