and the lieutenant.

480
00:18:57,770 --> 00:18:59,839
I could've sworn
you guys had chemistry.

481
00:18:59,872 --> 00:19:01,374
No.

482
00:19:01,408 --> 00:19:02,542
No chemistry.

483
00:19:02,575 --> 00:19:05,445
Well, win some,
lose some, I guess.
That's right.

484
00:19:05,478 --> 00:19:07,680
That is right.
Okay, I'm gonna call Lucifer.

485
00:19:07,714 --> 00:19:09,382
Awesome work. Hey, Lucifer,

486
00:19:09,416 --> 00:19:12,452
